name: Ziba

reviews.review_text:
Visited here last week. Really good place, just on the way to Baga beach! The vibe of the place is amazing. They have live music on weekends which elevates the vibe. They have an indoor as well as an outdoor seating.

The cocktails & food are excellent and totally worth the price. A must visit, especially over weekends!

It's a really well set up restaurant located just next to the busy lanes of North Goa and has a beautiful ambience. They offer spacious ambience overlooking beautiful fields, delicious oriental food, cocktails, live music and much more

We tried their special bloody Mary prawns for starters and we totally loved the unique flavours it had. Next we had their Vietnamese chilli fish and I loved every bite of it. The chonak fish was fresh and flavourful.
We also tried their Indonesian fried rice which was sweet, tangy. The chicken steak had tender chicken pieces tossed in flavourful sauce.
For drinks we had fresh orange juice, pineapple juice and lemon soda. It was really chilled and refreshing
For deserts, I had chocolate ice cream. Beautifully served and tasted heavenly.

They also have a live bar serving unique cocktails and mocktails and their ambience spanning over 3 floors is perfect for parties!!

The food was presented beautifully and the quantity was really good. The staff were welcoming and friendly. A must try place for weekend getaways in north goa!!

It was a lovely experience!!!
the food is very tasty and staff are very friendly.
They also do candlelight dinners on advance bookings.

Its a great place if you want to host birthday parties as they curate the menu as per your liking and very flexible.
Me and my friends had a great time..!!

description:
**Ziba – A Culinary Jewel in Arpora**

Nestled conveniently near the bustling lanes leading to Baga beach, Ziba has quickly become a cherished destination for both locals and tourists, boasting an impressive rating of 4.5 out of 5 from 646 enthusiastic reviewers. A consistent theme among patrons includes praise for refreshing **cocktails** (16 mentions) and exceptional **price** point value (15 mentions), alongside highlights of favorite dishes like **Viki** (7 mentions) and flavorful **dips** (7 mentions). This restaurant offers a vibrant mix of culinary delights that cater to diverse palates and celebratory vibes.

**Ambiance & Design**

Walking into Ziba, one is immediately struck by its captivating ambiance: a harmonious blend of indoor charm and outdoor vibrancy. The expansive layout features stunning views of serene fields, providing a picturesque backdrop for a leisurely meal. Images depict stylish décor with tasteful lighting that enhances the overall aesthetic, complemented by live music on weekends that establishes an uplifting atmosphere. With an impressive set-up spread across three floors, the space is tailor-made for gatherings, vibrant parties, or simply enjoying a relaxed dinner in good company.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

Ziba shines particularly in its culinary offerings, where unique flavors take center stage. Starters like the special **bloody Mary prawns** impress patrons with bold and inventive tastes, demonstrating the chef's creativity. The **Vietnamese chilli fish** is noted for its freshness and flavor, while the **Indonesian fried rice** stands out for its exciting sweet and tangy profile. Guests have marveled at dishes such as the **tender chicken steak**, which is generously coated in a rich sauce, and the delightful presentations are captured beautifully in customer-provided photos. Meanwhile, the dessert menu, featuring creamy **chocolate ice cream**, has left diners swooning over its deliciousness.

For those seeking lighter options, refreshing drinks like **fresh orange juice** and **pineapple juice** are perfectly chilled, enhancing the overall dining experience. Ziba accommodates dietary needs, offering a range of selections that are sure to satisfy various preferences.

**Customer Experience & Service**

The service at Ziba has received consistent accolades for being warm and welcoming. Reviewers emphasize their delight at the staff’s friendly demeanor, which adds to the overall enjoyable experience. Whether it's a birthday celebration with a customized menu or an intimate **candlelight dinner** arranged through advance booking, the restaurant’s flexibility caters to special occasions and casual outings alike. 

**Popularity & Reviews**

Ziba’s growing reputation is echoed across social media, where diners sing praises about their meals, the lively atmosphere, and attentive service. The buzz around this restaurant reflects its popularity as a must-visit spot during weekend getaways or fun gatherings in North Goa. Regular mentions of live music and special cocktails highlight why Ziba is a sought-after destination.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

The allure of Ziba is wonderfully illustrated through the vivid imagery provided by guests. Photographs reveal not just beautifully plated dishes, but also the encompassing environment—an inviting space alive with laughter, music, and the clinking of cocktail glasses. Each visual narrative invites potential diners to revel in a unique experience that goes beyond just a meal.

In summary, Ziba combines an enchanting setting, delectable cuisine, and attentive service, making it a culinary highlight in Arpora that you’ll want to share with friends and family. Whether you’re there for the cocktails, the food, or simply the ambiance, Ziba captures the essence of delightful dining. A visit to this gem surely promises a memorable experience!
